						p The world asked and IDX Boost delivered. After years in the business of creating real estate technology and through trial and error we bring to the industry a new breed of MLS search tools, leaving behind the old days of real estate. IDX Boost is fast, easy to use and affordable.
						Designed by UX (user experience) experts in collaboration with top producers, Realtors and agencies.

						p IDX Boost puts together the most comprehensive and beautiful MLS search tools. This platform gives real estate agents the ability to create a free, industry-leading website within a few minutes. Our super easy-to-use site customizer gives agents full control of the site’s look and feel and most importantly... its content.

						p Created for WordPress, IDX Boost gives users the flexibility to benefit from hundreds of third-party plugins, and its dashboard allows you to create content and use best practices for search engine optimization. A full-blown dashboard called IDX Analytics allows you to track your customer’s (and potential customer’s) journey through the website, showing visited listings, favorites and even saved searches. The dashboard also alerts you when a new visitor is live on the site.

						p We built IDX Boost after perfecting the system through the feedback of over 200 agents. The result is the most advanced and elegant real estate website with IDX search in the industry. No other company offers as much powerful technology in a single product. The new, fresh look combines with a responsive, mobile-friendly interface to appeal to agents in the competitive South Florida market and beyond.

